name: KUYLLUR No. 3 - AWKAYUK
description: Kuyllur is kechwa for star or heavenly body. This series of collectible reflections are meant to call our attention back to the daily cycle within the week. One kuyllur for each day of the week. A minute-long meditation to tune in with the unique energy of each day, which we can feel. Awkayuk is day three, also known as Tuesday. Artist is Espinosa on Twitter @spnsmtndsgn Lossless files (and other perks) available for collectors. 1080p24fps
